dcterms:description: MIMIC-III is one of the largest publicly available ICU datasets, comprising 38,597 distinct patients and a total of 53,423 ICU stays. It includes clinical time series data such as heart rate and glucose levels, which are used for mortality prediction tasks.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III
